\b\fs50 Th\f0\lang1033\'e0nh C\'f4ng \f3\'d0\f0\'e1ng N\f1\lang1066\u7875? T\u7915? Nh\u7919?ng B\f3\u432?\f1\u7899?c \f3\'d0i \'d0\f1\u7847?u Ti\f0\lang1033\'ean\b0\par
\fs30 HIEUTHUHAI b\f1\lang1066\u7855?t \f3\'f0\f1\u7847?u n\u7893?i l\f0\lang1033\'ean t\f1\lang1066\u7915? ch\f3\u432?\u417?ng tr\f0\lang1033\'ecnh King of Rap, n\f3\u417?i anh \'f0\f0\'e3 \f3\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7875? l\u7841?i \u7845?n t\f3\u432?\f1\u7907?ng m\u7841?nh nh\u7901? phong c\f0\lang1033\'e1ch tr\'ecnh di\f1\lang1066\u7877?n t\u7921? tin, ngo\u7841?i h\f0\lang1033\'ecnh s\'e1ng v\'e0 n\f3\'e3ng l\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7907?ng tr\f0\lang1033\'e0n \f3\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7847?y. Sau ch\f3\u432?\u417?ng tr\f0\lang1033\'ecnh, anh nhanh ch\'f3ng ghi d\f1\lang1066\u7845?u \u7845?n v\u7899?i nhi\u7873?u ca kh\f0\lang1033\'fac n\f1\lang1066\u7893?i ti\u7871?ng nh\f3\u432? Cua, Nghe Nh\u432? T\f0\lang1033\'ecnh Y\'eau, v\'e0 B\f1\lang1066\u7853?t Nh\u7841?c L\f0\lang1033\'ean. Nh\f1\lang1066\u7919?ng b\u7843?n hit n\f0\lang1033\'e0y \f3\'f0\f0\'e3 gi\'fap anh kh\f1\lang1066\u7859?ng \f3\'f0\f1\u7883?nh v\u7883? tr\f0\lang1033\'ed trong l\'f2ng kh\'e1n gi\f1\lang1066\u7843?, \f3\'f0\f1\u7863?c bi\u7879?t l\f0\lang1033\'e0 gi\f1\lang1066\u7899?i tr\u7867?. S\u7921? k\u7871?t h\u7907?p gi\u7919?a kh\u7843? n\f3\'e3ng rap t\f1\u7921? nhi\f0\lang1033\'ean, gi\f1\lang1066\u7885?ng ca cu\u7889?n h\f0\lang1033\'fat v\'e0 c\'e1ch truy\f1\lang1066\u7873?n t\u7843?i c\f0\lang1033\'e2u chuy\f1\lang1066\u7879?n \f3\'f0\u417?n gi\f1\u7843?n, g\u7847?n g\f3\u361?i \'f0\f0\lang1033\'e3 t\f1\lang1066\u7841?o n\f0\lang1033\'ean s\f1\lang1066\u7913?c h\f0\lang1033\'fat ri\'eang cho HIEUTHUHAI.\par
\par
Hai Y\f1\lang1066\u7871?u T\u7889? Thi\u7871?u H\u7909?t: Tu\u7893?i T\f0\lang1033\'e1c v\'e0 Kinh Nghi\f1\lang1066\u7879?m\par
D\f0\lang1033\'f9 c\'f3 \f3\'f0\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7907?c th\f0\lang1033\'e0nh c\'f4ng s\f1\lang1066\u7899?m, HIEUTHUHAI v\u7851?n c\f0\lang1033\'f2n m\f1\lang1066\u7897?t h\f0\lang1033\'e0nh tr\'ecnh d\'e0i ph\'eda tr\f3\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7899?c \f3\'f0\f1\u7875? ti\u7871?p t\u7909?c ph\f0\lang1033\'e1t tri\f1\lang1066\u7875?n b\u7843?n th\f0\lang1033\'e2n trong th\f1\lang1066\u7871? gi\u7899?i rap \f3\'f0\f1\u7847?y c\u7841?nh tranh. \f3\'d0i\f1\u7873?u anh c\f0\lang1033\'f2n thi\f1\lang1066\u7871?u kh\f0\lang1033\'f4ng ph\f1\lang1066\u7843?i l\f0\lang1033\'e0 t\'e0i n\f3\'e3ng, m\f0\'e0 ch\'ednh l\'e0 tu\f1\lang1066\u7893?i t\f0\lang1033\'e1c v\'e0 kinh nghi\f1\lang1066\u7879?m \f2\endash  hai y\f1\u7871?u t\u7889? s\u7869? gi\f0\lang1033\'fap anh \f3\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7841?t \f3\'f0\u432?\f1\u7907?c chi\u7873?u s\f0\lang1033\'e2u v\'e0 s\f1\lang1066\u7921? tr\f3\u432?\f1\u7903?ng th\f0\lang1033\'e0nh trong \'e2m nh\f1\lang1066\u7841?c.\par
\par
\b 1. Thi\u7871?u tu\u7893?i t\f0\lang1033\'e1c\b0\par
\par
Tu\f1\lang1066\u7893?i tr\u7867? l\f0\lang1033\'e0 m\f1\lang1066\u7897?t l\u7907?i th\u7871? l\u7899?n gi\f0\lang1033\'fap HIEUTHUHAI d\f1\lang1066\u7877? d\f0\lang1033\'e0ng k\f1\lang1066\u7871?t n\u7889?i v\u7899?i kh\f0\lang1033\'e1n gi\f1\lang1066\u7843? tr\u7867? v\f0\lang1033\'e0 mang l\f1\lang1066\u7841?i n\f3\'e3ng l\u432?\f1\u7907?ng m\u7899?i m\u7867? trong t\u7915?ng ca kh\f0\lang1033\'fac. Tuy nhi\'ean, tu\f1\lang1066\u7893?i tr\u7867? c\f3\u361?ng \'f0\f1\u7891?ng ngh\f3\u297?a v\f1\u7899?i vi\u7879?c anh c\f0\lang1033\'f2n thi\f1\lang1066\u7871?u tr\u7843?i nghi\u7879?m s\u7889?ng phong ph\f0\lang1033\'fa \f3\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7875? c\f0\lang1033\'f3 th\f1\lang1066\u7875? khai th\f0\lang1033\'e1c nh\f1\lang1066\u7919?ng ch\u7911? \f3\'f0\f1\u7873? s\f0\lang1033\'e2u s\f1\lang1066\u7855?c h\f3\u417?n trong \f0\lang1033\'e2m nh\f1\lang1066\u7841?c. So v\u7899?i nh\u7919?ng rapper k\u7923? c\u7921?u, HIEUTHUHAI c\f0\lang1033\'f3 th\f1\lang1066\u7875? thi\u7871?u \f3\'f0i nh\f1\u7919?ng g\f0\lang1033\'f3c nh\'ecn gi\'e0u tr\f1\lang1066\u7843?i nghi\u7879?m ho\u7863?c s\u7921? t\u7915?ng tr\u7843?i gi\f0\lang1033\'fap truy\f1\lang1066\u7873?n t\u7843?i nh\u7919?ng th\f0\lang1033\'f4ng \f3\'f0i\f1\lang1066\u7879?p ph\u7913?c t\u7841?p v\f0\lang1033\'e0 nhi\f1\lang1066\u7873?u t\u7847?ng \f0\lang1033\'fd ngh\f3\u297?a h\u417?n. Nh\u432?ng c\u361?ng ch\f0\'ednh v\'ec c\'f2n tr\f1\lang1066\u7867?, anh c\f0\lang1033\'f3 th\f1\lang1066\u7901?i gian \f3\'f0\f1\u7875? ti\u7871?p t\u7909?c h\u7885?c h\u7887?i v\f0\lang1033\'e0 tr\f3\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7903?ng th\f0\lang1033\'e0nh, mang \f3\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7871?n nhi\u7873?u g\f0\lang1033\'f3c nh\'ecn \f3\'f0a d\f1\lang1066\u7841?ng h\f3\u417?n trong t\u432?\u417?ng lai.\par
\par
\b 2. Thi\f1\u7871?u kinh nghi\u7879?m\b0\par
\par
Trong rap, kinh nghi\u7879?m kh\f0\lang1033\'f4ng ch\f1\lang1066\u7881? n\u7857?m \u7903? tu\u7893?i t\f0\lang1033\'e1c m\'e0 c\'f2n \f1\lang1066\u7903? k\u7929? n\f3\'e3ng k\f1\u7929? thu\u7853?t v\f0\lang1033\'e0 kh\f1\lang1066\u7843? n\f3\'e3ng s\f0\lang1033\'e1ng t\f1\lang1066\u7841?o. S\u7921? linh ho\u7841?t trong gieo v\u7847?n, c\f0\lang1033\'e1ch t\f1\lang1066\u7841?o d\u7921?ng flow ph\u7913?c t\u7841?p v\f0\lang1033\'e0 s\'e2u s\f1\lang1066\u7855?c, c\f0\lang1033\'f9ng vi\f1\lang1066\u7879?c x\f0\lang1033\'e2y d\f1\lang1066\u7921?ng m\u7897?t phong c\f0\lang1033\'e1ch ri\'eang bi\f1\lang1066\u7879?t c\u7847?n \f3\'f0\u432?\f1\u7907?c m\f0\lang1033\'e0i gi\f3\u361?a qua th\f1\lang1066\u7901?i gian. Kinh nghi\u7879?m s\u7869? gi\f0\lang1033\'fap anh ho\'e0n thi\f1\lang1066\u7879?n c\f0\lang1033\'e1c k\f1\lang1066\u7929? thu\u7853?t bi\u7875?u di\u7877?n v\f0\lang1033\'e0 s\'e1ng t\f1\lang1066\u7841?o nh\u7841?c, t\u7915? \f3\'f0\f0\lang1033\'f3 t\f1\lang1066\u7841?o ra nh\u7919?ng t\f0\lang1033\'e1c ph\f1\lang1066\u7849?m mang \f3\'f0\f1\u7853?m d\u7845?u \u7845?n c\f0\lang1033\'e1 nh\'e2n h\f3\u417?n. Vi\f1\lang1066\u7879?c ti\u7871?p t\u7909?c r\f0\lang1033\'e8n luy\f1\lang1066\u7879?n v\f0\lang1033\'e0 h\f1\lang1066\u7907?p t\f0\lang1033\'e1c v\f1\lang1066\u7899?i c\f0\lang1033\'e1c ngh\f1\lang1066\u7879? s\f3\u297? kh\f0\lang1033\'e1c s\f1\lang1066\u7869? l\f0\lang1033\'e0 c\f3\u417? h\f1\lang1066\u7897?i \f3\'f0\f1\u7875? HIEUTHUHAI h\u7885?c h\u7887?i v\f0\lang1033\'e0 ph\'e1t tri\f1\lang1066\u7875?n.\par
\par
\b\f3\'d0\f1\u7883?nh H\f3\u432?\f1\u7899?ng Ph\f0\lang1033\'e1t Tri\f1\lang1066\u7875?n\b0\par
\f3\'d0\f1\u7889?i v\u7899?i m\u7897?t ngh\u7879? s\f3\u297? tr\f1\u7867? nh\f3\u432? HIEUTHUHAI, vi\f1\u7879?c \f0\lang1033\'fd th\f1\lang1066\u7913?c \f3\'f0\u432?\f1\u7907?c nh\u7919?ng y\u7871?u t\u7889? m\f0\lang1033\'ecnh c\'f2n thi\f1\lang1066\u7871?u ch\f0\lang1033\'ednh l\'e0 b\f3\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7899?c \f3\'f0i \'f0\f1\u7847?u ti\f0\lang1033\'ean \f3\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7875? ti\u7871?n xa h\f3\u417?n trong s\f1\u7921? nghi\u7879?p. S\u7921? ph\f0\lang1033\'e1t tri\f1\lang1066\u7875?n trong \f0\lang1033\'e2m nh\f1\lang1066\u7841?c c\u7847?n c\f0\lang1033\'f3 th\f1\lang1066\u7901?i gian v\f0\lang1033\'e0 kh\'f4ng ng\f1\lang1066\u7915?ng r\f0\lang1033\'e8n luy\f1\lang1066\u7879?n, v\f0\lang1033\'e0 s\f1\lang1066\u7921? nghi\u7879?p c\u7911?a m\u7897?t rapper kh\f0\lang1033\'f4ng ch\f1\lang1066\u7881? xoay quanh th\f0\lang1033\'e0nh c\'f4ng nhanh ch\'f3ng m\'e0 c\'f2n l\'e0 h\'e0nh tr\'ecnh kh\'e1m ph\'e1, t\'edch l\f3\u361?y kinh nghi\f1\lang1066\u7879?m v\f0\lang1033\'e0 h\f1\lang1066\u7885?c h\u7887?i. C\f0\lang1033\'e1c rapper k\f1\lang1066\u7923? c\u7921?u trong n\f3\u432?\f1\u7899?c v\f0\lang1033\'e0 qu\f1\lang1066\u7889?c t\u7871? th\f3\u432?\f1\u7901?ng ch\u7881? \f3\'f0\f1\u7841?t \f3\'f0\f1\u7871?n \f3\'f0\f1\u7881?nh cao khi \f3\'f0\f0\lang1033\'e3 tr\f1\lang1066\u7843?i qua nh\u7919?ng n\f3\'e3m th\f0\lang1033\'e1ng d\'e0i g\f1\lang1066\u7855?n b\f0\lang1033\'f3 v\f1\lang1066\u7899?i ngh\u7873? v\f0\lang1033\'e0 v\f3\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7907?t qua nhi\u7873?u th\u7917? th\f0\lang1033\'e1ch. HIEUTHUHAI ho\'e0n to\'e0n c\'f3 ti\f1\lang1066\u7873?m n\f3\'e3ng \'f0\f1\u7841?t \f3\'f0\u432?\f1\u7907?c \f3\'f0i\f1\u7873?u n\f0\lang1033\'e0y n\f1\lang1066\u7871?u anh ti\u7871?p t\u7909?c trau d\u7891?i v\f0\lang1033\'e0 th\f1\lang1066\u7917? nghi\u7879?m b\u7843?n th\f0\lang1033\'e2n trong nhi\f1\lang1066\u7873?u phong c\f0\lang1033\'e1ch v\'e0 ch\f1\lang1066\u7911? \f3\'f0\f1\u7873? kh\f0\lang1033\'e1c nhau.\par
\par
\b K\f1\lang1066\u7871?t Lu\u7853?n\b0\par
HIEUTHUHAI \f3\'f0\f0\lang1033\'e3 \f3\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7841?t \f3\'f0\u432?\f1\u7907?c nhi\u7873?u th\f0\lang1033\'e0nh c\'f4ng m\'e0 b\f1\lang1066\u7845?t c\u7913? ngh\u7879? s\f3\u297? tr\f1\u7867? n\f0\lang1033\'e0o c\f3\u361?ng m\u417? \u432?\f1\lang1066\u7899?c, nh\f3\u432?ng tu\f1\u7893?i t\f0\lang1033\'e1c v\'e0 kinh nghi\f1\lang1066\u7879?m v\u7851?n l\f0\lang1033\'e0 nh\f1\lang1066\u7919?ng y\u7871?u t\u7889? m\f0\lang1033\'e0 anh c\f1\lang1066\u7847?n b\u7893? sung \f3\'f0\f1\u7875? ho\f0\lang1033\'e0n thi\f1\lang1066\u7879?n b\u7843?n th\f0\lang1033\'e2n. \f3\'d0\f1\lang1066\u7889?i v\u7899?i kh\f0\lang1033\'e1n gi\f1\lang1066\u7843?, vi\u7879?c \f3\'f0\f1\u7891?ng h\f0\lang1033\'e0nh c\'f9ng HIEUTHUHAI tr\'ean h\'e0nh tr\'ecnh ph\'e1t tri\f1\lang1066\u7875?n l\f0\lang1033\'e0 m\f1\lang1066\u7897?t tr\u7843?i nghi\u7879?m th\f0\lang1033\'fa v\f1\lang1066\u7883?, khi ch\u7913?ng ki\u7871?n t\u7915?ng b\f3\u432?\f1\u7899?c tr\f3\u432?\f1\u7903?ng th\f0\lang1033\'e0nh v\'e0 t\f1\lang1066\u7915?ng s\u7843?n ph\u7849?m ng\f0\lang1033\'e0y c\'e0ng ch\f1\lang1066\u7845?t l\f3\u432?\f1\u7907?ng h\f3\u417?n c\f1\u7911?a anh. V\u7899?i t\f0\lang1033\'e0i n\f3\'e3ng v\f0\'e0 s\f1\lang1066\u7921? n\u7895? l\u7921?c kh\f0\lang1033\'f4ng ng\f1\lang1066\u7915?ng, HIEUTHUHAI ch\u7855?c ch\u7855?n s\u7869? c\f0\lang1033\'f2n ti\f1\lang1066\u7871?n xa, ti\u7871?p t\u7909?c ghi d\u7845?u \u7845?n trong l\f0\lang1033\'e0ng nh\f1\lang1066\u7841?c rap Vi\u7879?t Nam v\f0\lang1033\'e0 mang \f3\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7871?n nh\u7919?ng s\f0\lang1033\'e1ng t\'e1c \f3\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7847?y c\u7843?m h\u7913?ng cho ng\f3\u432?\f1\u7901?i nghe.\f4\fs17\lang1033\par
